Whereas it is known that the Rt Hon member Anthony Blair MP.,QC &c is a big fan of popular, ethnic, and traditional scottish music and dance;
And furthermore, that said Hon Member is reliably alleged to groove and boogie with the best of them cool dudes;
Thereby these humble petitioner grovellingly propose that Tony (aka PM (UK) )
does attend said festivity and get down to it, like OK?  (&c)
PS, it would be really nice as well if Tony could also give up weapons of mass destruction, abandon the rather silly ID cards plan and stop sending asylum seekers back to fascist regimes like Zimbabwe, but maybe that is too much to hope for.
